<adietrichs> Reminder: EIP-4844 Readiness Check breakout call in ~18 hours!
Agenda: https://ethereum-magicians.org/t/rollcall-breakout-1-eip-4844-readiness-check/18226
Zoom: https://ethereumfoundation.zoom.us/j/83134379888?pwd=kSUBgrIwYYfiNQfoYH2sOAxCptPPTZ.1

We will have two people from EF Devops deeply involved in the Dencun testing process join the call as well. The aim is to have this be a useful checkin for L2 teams that are planning to become blob consumers in the next few months - so I hope to see many of you tomorrow!

And if you have any specific topics that you'd like to discuss tomorrow, leave a comment in the agenda thread over on Ethereum Magicians.
